>In essence, DAD is performed at the BT level.

Well, perhaps strictly speaking not at the BT level, if you think about BT'=
s protocol layers, but rather by support software that decides about establ=
ishing BT connections. I clarified this to the draft.

>> -> IPv6 Link-Local address for a node is generated from the Bluetooth
>> address used for the Bluetooth connection (and for the duration of the=20
