We submitted a updated draft about IPv6 over NFC.

https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-hong-6lo-ipv6-over-nfc/


In Toronto meeting, we had valuable comments after presentation.

Among them, Suresh gave a comment that detail address mapping is needed.

In a updated draft, we believe that the Suresh's comment is addressed by
adding

additional section 4.7 (Unicast Address Mapping) and 4.8 (Multicast Address
Mapping).

Other typos are also corrected.


Any comments and feedbacks are welcome.


Thanks.


Best regards.
